Package com.example.cmscdocs

Class XWPFRunCustom

java.lang.Object
com.example.cmscdocs.XWPFRunCustom
public class XWPFRunCustom extends Object
This class is a utility based class that helps with the Controller class' XWPFRun customizations. This class initially extends the XWPFRun class from Apache POI-OOXMl but due to certain modularization technicalities, it was then instead used as a standalone class which primarily consists of static methods.
Author:
Nathan Tablang

      public static void setCustomHeadingSettings​(org.apache.poi.xwpf.usermodel.XWPFRun line)
